title: 4 Rare 80s Albums [Part 32] Your Requests
description:
Four records out of your requests. If you were one of those requesting any of these Lps, I hope you enjoy it and help seeding. Now how I rate them:

Academy - The Collection  

5 Stars!! I never understood why they did not make it big. Their sound was way superior over some "mainstream" bands back then.


Flaming Mussolinis - Watching the Film [1985] 

4 Stars, some great songs here but gets 4 star for two songs I don't like


Private Lives - Prejudice & Pride [1984] 

5 Stars! Awesome and consistent througout the lp.


The Painted Word - Lovelife 

5 Stars! New Romantic at its best. What a shame they also remained so obscure.
